{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You wake up in a strange place that seems frozen in time, with a simple goal: explore, find clues, and escape. You won\u2019t encounter monsters or sudden scares; instead, the terror comes from the atmosphere and the tension of not knowing if you\u2019ll find a way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game challenges your sense of direction and creates a feeling of loneliness and mystery in every corner. There\u2019s no background music, only ambient sounds and echoes that change with each room.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The experience is immersive, realistic, and challenging. As you explore, you\u2019ll notice the hotel shifting around you, offering a new and unique experience in every place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by backrooms and liminal spaces, <strong>Hotel 188</strong> invites you to get lost and uncover secrets in every corner.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738111779","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322980/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738111779","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322980/716e2fb34b2b7d22db3fb6267ea36f84d054ae26/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738111779","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322980/716e2fb34b2b7d22db3fb6267ea36f84d054ae26/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738111779","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3363020,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You wake up in a strange place that seems frozen in time, with a simple goal: explore, find clues, and escape. You won\u2019t encounter monsters or sudden scares;